- Sent2Vec server asynchronously decoupled with SQS queue, scaled with auto-scaling and CloudWatch based on queue length
- No multi-AZ recovery support (everytihng runs in a single AZ)
- Run sent2vec-server Docker image on instance startup
- Autoscaling launch configuration user data
